						 CLEVELAND CREATIVE = ONLINE MARKETING 
						 
							 
								 
									 To create a financial success in the online age, an entrepreneur or business must tell an engaging story directly to people who are interested in that story. 
									 Make the best widget on the planet but tell a poor story about that widget, and the world pays little attention to your widget. 
									 Or tell the story to people who couldn't care less about widgets, and even the best widget business dies a slow, painful death. 
									 But tell an engaging story directly to people actively looking for information about widgets, and your widget business booms. (Assuming, of course, the story is presented professionally, has the right offer, and provides a simple and secure way to 'buy now!' or 'learn more!') 
									 Cleveland Creative tells engaging stories. We help entrepreneurs and small businesses craft those stories to reach their target audience, and we deliver that message through search, through e-commerce, through creative presentation, and through direct and online marketing. 
									 We combine imaginative, efficient selling ideas with up-to-date marketing strategies and professional presentation to reach your target affordably. To engage your current and potential customers in the right way, at the right time. To SELL. 
